{"tid":758618,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股東集體起訴朱克伯格 指控fb誤導股東","createTime":"2018-07-28T01:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T08:48:34.000Z","uid":32938,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"66e04d26cc1b9620a11f3e0eebf2d5f225f828de","tid":758618,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T01:07:26.000Z","msg":"Facebook(fb)業績令市場失望，有股東入稟控告Facebook及創辦人朱克伯格(Mark Zuckerberg)。<br />\n<br />\n股東卡古里斯向曼哈頓聯邦法院入稟，指Facebook、朱克伯格及首席財務官魏納作出誤導陳述，未有披露收入增長放緩、營業利潤率下跌，以及活躍用戶人數下降等資訊。<br />\n<br />\n卡古里斯指出，Facebook在周三公布的業績令市場震驚，股價單日下跌19%，令股東約1200億美元的財富蒸發；同時，尋求這宗案件取得集體訴訟，並要求賠償。<br />\n<br />\n集體訴訟文件指出，Facebook和一些其他的被告發布了一系列虛假和誤導性的陳述，並未向投資者披露關於公司業務、運營和前景的重大不利事實。"},{"pid":"aed3aeca7d47784eb23dd1c8cf5d85dce2248066","tid":758618,"uid":77936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T01:19:02.000Z","msg":"俾佢再告多吓 佢咪再蝕多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecae3860bdee8213abd6a02ba67d265a30ed42ef","tid":758618,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aed3aeca7d47784eb23dd1c8cf5d85dce2248066","tid":758618,"uid":77936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T01:19:02.000Z","msg":"俾佢再告多吓 佢咪再蝕多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T01:22:06.000Z","msg":"沽爆佢咪得"},{"pid":"3a13fe9272e99f37b5e58b1bdd917dd837e216c2","tid":758618,"uid":53429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2bc9d3b5bbde3a45f3cf310d7f890541105c0f","tid":758618,"uid":85556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"內幕交易先犯法喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e99301c4d91b4035f1356d03f528cefb108f80","tid":758618,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f2bc9d3b5bbde3a45f3cf310d7f890